# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4100/api/v1/users
@int = {{$randomInt 1000 9999}}
@authToken = {{login.response.body.data}}

### Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### Add a user
POST {{baseUrl}}/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
    "firstname": "{{int}}Member",
    "middlename": "Test",
    "lastname": "User",
    "email": "{{int}}@example.com",
    "password": "{{int}}",
    "joinDate": "2018-01-01",
    "phone": "+255755{{int}}00",
    "level": "member"
}


### Get user details
GET {{baseUrl}}/5f888c4cb19869774818060b
Authorization: {{authToken}}

 
### Update Specific User Details
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/5f885ee0943d0c74e49f5eb4 HTTP/1.1
